These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-1::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: marigold, poppy, orchid, tulip, bellflower
The people have 5 different hobbies: collecting, chess, fishing, skydiving, filmmaking
The people use 5 different means of transport: airplane, helicopter, ship, taxi, train
House: cape-cod, modern, farmhouse, art-deco, craftsman
 1. the craftsman house is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
 2. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
 3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
 4. the person who growsorchid is the person who growsorchid##1
 5. the cape-cod house is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 6. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
 7. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
 8. the person who growstulip is on the right of the art-deco house##1
 9. the person who growstulip is on the far right##1
10. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
11. the person who growsbellflower is between the person driving the helicopter and the person who's hobby is filmmaking##2
12. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
13. the person driving the train is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |    5     |
| Flower      | marigold        | poppy | bellflower     | orchid   | tulip |
| Hobby   | fishing     | chess      | skydiving | filmmaking   | collecting    |
| Transport   | taxi  | helicopter     | airplane | ship | train  |
| House           | modern | farmhouse      | craftsman     | art-deco   | cape-cod     |

