.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-2::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  coach, doctor, police-officer, pilot, bartender
There are 5 different favourite colors: aquamarine, ebony, mauve, blood-red, green
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: march, january, august, february, may
House: wooden, colonial, tower, palace, farmhouse
 1. the farmhouse house is in the middle##1
 2. the person who likes green is on the left of the coach##1
 3. the doctor is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
 4. the bartender is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 5. the colonial house is between the person who's birthday is in march and the person who likes green##2
 6. the palace house is the doctor##1
 7. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the wooden house##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in august is the person who likes blood-red##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the doctor##1
10. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1
11. the person who's birthday is in august is the police-officer##1
12. the colonial house is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Job         | pilot | coach | bartender    | doctor  | police-officer    |
| Color   | green    | ebony       | mauve      | aquamarine | blood-red        |
| Birthday   | may   | january     | march    | february  | august     |
| House     | tower    | colonial | farmhouse | palace | wooden |

