 7. the palace house is on the left of the person who likes red##1
 8. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
 9. the ranch-style house is on the far left##1
10. the person who likes aquamarine is the person eating cherry##1
11. the mexican is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
12. the polish is on the right of the palace house##1
13. the person who likes light-blue is between the person eating zucchini and the mexican##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4       |       5       |
