.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-4::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, davidoff, old-henry, swisher, vegafina
There are 5 different favourite beverages: milk, water, lemonade, soy-milk, almond-milk
The people use 5 different means of transport: trike, motorbike, tram, snowmobile, subway
House: palace, townhouse, farmhouse, futuristic, colonial
 1. the townhouse house is on the far left##1
 2. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
 3. the davidoff-smoker is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
 4. the colonial house is between the person driving the snowmobile and the swisher-smoker##2
 5. the davidoff-smoker is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
 6. the person driving the subway is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
 7. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
 8. the person drinking almond-milk is the person driving the motorbike##1
 9. the person driving the subway is in the middle##1
10. the person driving the snowmobile is the palace house##1
11. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
12. the palace house is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
13. the person driving the motorbike is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5     |
| Cigar          | vegafina  | old-henry     | swisher   | davidoff     | baccarat |
| Beverage         | almond-milk | milk    | lemonade  | soy-milk | water   |
| Transport   | motorbike        | trike    | subway     | tram     | snowmobile    |
| House   | townhouse    | farmhouse | futuristic | colonial | palace   |

