 2. the person who likes turquise is on the left of the vegafina-smoker##1
 3. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the prince-smoker##1
 4. the person watching horror movies is between the dunhill-smoker and the person who likes pink##2
 5. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1
 6. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person who likes turquise##1
 7. the person watching western movies is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
 8. the owner of the goat is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1
 9. the person watching drama movies is on the far right##1
10. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
11. the person who likes pink is on the left of the person who likes ebony##1
12. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
13. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |       2       |       3       |       4       |    5     |
| Movie-Genre   | western       | epic       | zombie   | horror      | drama    |
