 2. the person who growsmarigold is on the far left##1
 3. the fan gospel is the person who growsiris##1
 4. the fan dubstep is between the person drinking 7up and the person playing scrabble##2
 5. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
 6. the person drinking almond-milk is in the middle##1
 7. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person playing go##1
 8. the person playing snooker is on the far right##1
 9. the fan ambient is the person playing backgammon##1
10. the fan techno is on the left of the person who growslily##1
11. the fan ambient is on the right of the person playing go##1
12. the fan techno is the person drinking coffee##1
13. the fan dubstep is on the left of the person playing snooker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |     4      |      5       |
