 6. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
 7. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
 8. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person eating potato##1
 9. the person eating watermelon is the ritmeester-smoker##1
10. the blend-smoker is between the montecristo-smoker and the person playing bridge##2
11. the person drinking milk is the person eating pear##1
12. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1

