.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-17::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: february, june, april, january, march
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: western, animation, epic, satire, disaster
There are 5 different favourite colors: red, grey, coral, emerald, blood-red
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: funk, salsa, ambient, r&b, electronic
 1. the person who likes blood-red is between the fan salsa and the person who likes grey##2
 2. the person who likes coral is on the left of the person who likes emerald##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in june is the person watching satire movies##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
 5. the fan salsa is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 6. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the fan salsa##1
 7. the fan funk is on the right of the fan electronic##1
 8. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 9. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
10. the person who likes coral is on the far left##1
11. the fan ambient is between the person who likes coral and the person watching epic movies##2
12. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
13. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5      |
| Birthday    | april       | january    | march | june  | february        |
| Movie-Genre       | disaster | western | epic  | satire | animation    |
| Color       | coral        | emerald   | grey  | blood-red   | red |
| Music-Genre   | r&b       | ambient      | electronic      | funk | salsa  |

