.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-18::.
House: cottage, craftsman, palace, tower, victorian
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, fonseca, cain, aristoff, siglo
There 5 different types of food: lemon, lime, cauliflower, grapefruit, blueberry
5 different games are played: backgammon, scrabble, poker, whist, bridge
 1. the person playing poker is on the left of the person eating lime##1
 2. the aristoff-smoker is between the person eating cauliflower and the cain-smoker##2
 3. the tower house is the aristoff-smoker##1
 4. the person eating blueberry is on the right of the person playing whist##1
 5. the person eating lemon is in the middle##1
 6. the tower house is between the siglo-smoker and the person playing scrabble##2
 7. the person playing whist is the palace house##1
 8. the cottage house is the person playing poker##1
 9. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1
10. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the person eating cauliflower##1
11. the cain-smoker is the person eating lime##1
12. the person eating grapefruit is on the far left##1
13. the victorian house is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3     |    4     |     5      |
| House      | cottage      | craftsman         | tower      | palace | victorian     |
| Cigar           | fonseca | cain | aristoff | siglo    | tiparillo  |
| Food   | grapefruit  | lime    | lemon | cauliflower    | blueberry |
| Game   | poker  | scrabble        | backgammon   | whist    | bridge     |

