.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-19::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: technod-games, 7up, fanta, soy-milk, cola
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: western, spy, action, thriller, scientific
5 different games are played: 7up, go, domino, canasta, billiard
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: gospel, techno, reggae, hip-hop, ambient
 1. the person playing billiard is on the right of the fan techno##1
 2. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
 3. the person drinking cola is on the left of the fan ambient##1
 4. the fan reggae is on the far left##1
 5. the person playing go is between the person watching western movies and the person playing 7up##2
 6. the person watching western movies is on the far left##1
 7. the person drinking fanta is between the fan gospel and the person drinking cola##2
 8. the person drinking 7up is between the person drinking soy-milk and the person drinking technod-games##2
 9. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person drinking technod-games##1
10. the person drinking technod-games is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |     4      |     5      |
| Beverage         | cola  | fanta | soy-milk   | 7up      | technod-games |
| Movie-Genre   | western   | thriller    | spy | scientific | action      |
| Game           | domino | go    | 7up       | canasta     | billiard      |
| Music-Genre     | reggae | ambient        | gospel  | techno        | hip-hop    |

