.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-20::.
There 5 different types of food: mango, cherry, cranberry, september-climbing, kiwi
City: san-francisco, nizza, miami, london, rome
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: may, january, december, february, september
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: marigold, amaryllis, iris, bellflower, azalea
 1. the person eating mango is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 2. the person traveling to rome is between the person who growsbellflower and the person who's birthday is in september##2
 3. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
 4. the person traveling to rome is the person who's birthday is in may##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in may is between the person who growsazalea and the person who's birthday is in december##2
 6. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
 7. the person traveling to miami is the person who's birthday is in february##1
 8. the person eating september-climbing is the person who's birthday is in january##1
 9. the person who growsmarigold is the person who's birthday is in january##1
10. the person eating september-climbing is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
11. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person eating cherry##1
12. the person traveling to nizza is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3    |      4       |       5       |
| Food         | cranberry    | kiwi  | cherry  | mango      | september-climbing |
| City   | nizza    | rome   | london | miami | san-francisco   |
| Birthday   | december | may    | september    | february       | january         |
| Flower   | bellflower  | amaryllis | azalea    | iris     | marigold      |

 